stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> planned
  planned --> skipped: --resume and complete output exists
  planned --> running: stage starts
  running --> success: temp output renamed atomically
  running --> failed: parse/preprocess/validate error caught
  success --> manifest_success: append status=success
  skipped --> manifest_skipped: append status=skipped
  failed --> manifest_failed: append status=failed with error text
  manifest_success --> [*]
  manifest_skipped --> [*]
  manifest_failed --> [*]
